---
title: Cheesy-Peas-y Mushroom and Shrimp Ravioli with Golden Panko-Parm Topping
description: Get ready for an unexpected but familiar flavour application with this mushroom ravioli dinner topped with shrimp.  A riff on the classic Italian cacio e pepe, we've kept the cheese but traded the pepper for the sweet pop of green peas!
